{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "à takka tas KUNGS:\nNo-eij eekſch ta Kehnina\nno Juha Namma/ un\nrunna tur ſcho Wahrdn."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fakki: Klauti ta KUNG-\nGA Wahrdn/ tu Kehninsch no\nJuha/ kas tu fehdi us Dahwi-\nda Gohda-Krehſlu/ Tu/ un tawi\nKalpi/ un tawi Laudis/ kaszaunr\ntchahm Wahrtim ee-eet."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS:\nNeffeet Teetu un Taifnibu/ un\nisglahbeet to Aplaupitu no ta\nApbehdinataja Rohkas/ un ne\nplehfeet to Swechtineku/ Bah-\nrinu/ nedś Atraitni/ ne darrajt\nWarras-Darbu/ un ne iſteijeet\nſchaî Weetā nenoseedsigu Affini."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kad juhs ſcho Leetn dar-\nriſeet/ tad ee-ees zaur tcha Nam-\nma Wahrtim Kehnini/ kas us\nDahwida Gohda-Krehſlu teh-\ndehs/ un brauks ar Ratteem\nun Sirgeem/ tik labbi wiſch/\nka winna Kalpi/ un winna Lau-\ndis."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja juhs ſchohs Wahrdus ne grihbat klaufiht/ tad ef-\nmu es pee ſew paſcha ſwehrejs/\nfakka tas KUNGS: Ka ſchim\nNamnam buhs par pohſtu Wee-\ntu tapt."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nno ta Namma ta Kehnina Ju-\nda: Gileada tu man eſti eekſch\nLibbanns ta Galwa/ ja es tikai\ntewi ne par Tuſhneti darru/ un\ntohs Pilſtahtus bes Eedſihwo-\ntajeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es eezelfſchu pahr tewi"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ees daufs Pagann\nſchim Pilſfahtam tezzen/ un ſaz-\nzihs weens uhs ohtru: Kapelz\nirr tas KUNGS ta darrijs\nſchim leelam Pilſfahtam?"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee ſazzihs: Tadeht ka\ntee irr atſtabjuſchi to Derribu ta\nKUNGA fawa Deewa/ un\npreekſch zitteein Deeweem klan-\nniſchees/ un teem kalpojſcht."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne raudajt pahr to No-\nmirnuſchu/ un ne noscheblojeet\nwinnu/ raudajt raudadam pahr\nto/ kas aiseet/ jo tas ne atgree-\nſifees atpakat/ ka tas fawn\nDsintas-Senmi warretu re-\ndjeht."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nno Salluma/ ta Dehta Josijus/\nta Kehnina no Juha/ kas fawa\nTehwa Josijus Weetā walda/\nkas no ſchahs Weetas irr ats-\nqahjts/ wiſch ne atgreeſifees\nwairs atpakat."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tai Weetā/ kurp tee\nwinnu irr aisweduſchi/ wiſch\nnomirs/ un ſcho Senmi wiſch\nwairs ne redſehs."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wai tam! kas fawn\nNamimu ar Metaimibu uſtaita/\nun fawas augſtas Iſtabas ar\nmetaifnu Buhſchanu/ kas tawu\nTuwaku leeſ welti strahdaht/ un\nne dohd winnam fawn Algu."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas dohma/ es uſtaiff-\nschu ſew weenu kohti augſtu"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
